      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/240a7dfccb5e733342507e896ab68a90_1784959409960992685.png",
                "key": "西風劍術．白",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西風劍術．白"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">陽華</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/4c999a92de43cfba640c30b45c782fc9_3245869829768639555.png",
                "key": "創生法．擬造陽華",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "創生法．擬造陽華"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">陽華</span>在場，就使此傷害+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/42d2ae5af0169e6938febe18de57d31a_2490514253421541073.png",
                "key": "誕生式．大地之潮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "誕生式．大地之潮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召喚物在場時：</span>我方角色進行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">下落攻擊</span>時少花費一個<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無色元素</span>。(每回合1次)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_80862319859143776.png",
                "key": "陽華",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/02297af9d3309f3e4e40eca8911a19f6_5973911624164554830.png",
                "title": "陽華"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_4696113294685493738.png",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">下落攻擊</span></strong></p><p>角色被切換為「出戰角色」後，本回合內的下一個戰鬥行動若為「普通攻擊」，則被視為「下落攻擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無色元素</span></strong></p><p>可以用任意類型的元素骰子組合，來支付此類費用。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6855664197579612653.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
